songs.title: Head On
songs.lyrics:

Bit', yeah, I

Hop off a jet, lookin' to see where I'm at, uh
Over two bodies we done stretched, got her head on, wet
Rip my pockets, I can't let, got her head on bet, uh

I'm him, cookin' the yay, did without workin' a sweat
